title: Person of Interest 2x22 God Mode "Can you hear me ? "
author: George Finch
comment: I'm having chills, the soundtrack, the machine speaking, Root's look and smile and finally the "absolutely"
I would Really Love to see a SuperCut of all the God Mode Scenes. Specifically the UI from the machines Perspective.
How did I miss this scene before?! Team Root all the way <3
